Package: decarbmonitoring
Title: Create indicators relevant for the decarb monitoring of the Kanton of Zürich
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bosch", "Philipp", email = "philipp.bosch@statistik.ji.zh.ch", role = "cre"),
    person("Grobe", "Corinna", email = "corinna.grobe@statistik.ji.zh.ch", role = "aut"),
    person("Lo Russo", "Thomas", email = "thomas.lorusso@statistik.ji.zh.ch", role = "aut"))
Description: This package contains functions to perform the whole ETL (extract, transform, load) pipeline 
    for each indicator of the "Dekarbonisierungsmonitoring" of the Kanton of Zürich.
